r />\n案情指，去年萬聖節大批示威者七時半在旺角一帶堵路及縱火，警方約在晚上10時半採取行動驅散人群，並截停李，在他身上找到一張寫有「正義必勝」的海報，警員其後在被告棄置後巷的背包內搜出5枚汽油彈。<br />\n<br />\n法庭記者：蕭文軒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:12:37.000Z","msg":"一條片睇晒楊岳橋立法會表現<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2021857\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2021857</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"141efba77f693e7cf5dcbb67e7cc5c3fbd855afb","tid":2022273,"uid":116568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:12:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33e8b10ecfe538eb57596317388a9a63b1895587","tid":2022273,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:12:57.000Z","msg":"藏有已經12個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d72cc8547758f6a303620241a1964b0d1c6a124","tid":2022273,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:13:27.000Z","msg":"表弟？真定假？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"decfbcc6fc244d4cacda8e25b715f0aa9c9a55d0","tid":2022273,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7bbaa00358c6ad42df3ef954da4266d75eb876a4","tid":2022273,"uid":198216,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f9780b8d0433c226afa1bf6fc2cfb057cc991d0f","tid":2022273,"uid":254022,"like":83,"dislike":3,"score":80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T09:07:29.000Z","msg":"關水煎包咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁水煎包本人黃定藍？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T10:08:42.000Z","msg":"發夢見過佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T11:13:45.000Z","msg":"咁佢有冇案件重演？"},{"pid":"529abe2b1f6a6be7228dc058b79e600155664a3b","tid":2022273,"uid":12185,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4dba6610f689cba53a690814128bdf8ab3ad46d0","tid":2022273,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6223be3a6e043c142ba7441ed6c2d179a0c